Package View_Controller

Class ApptTableViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • View_Controller.ApptTableViewController
  • public class ApptTableViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    Appointment Table View screen displays list of all scheduled appointments in table view. In this screen, user will be able to select buttons for going back to previous screen, adding/updating/deleting appointments.
